Package com.cafean.client.ui.navigator

Class NavigatorRootNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultMutableTreeNode
      • com.cafean.client.ui.navigator.NavigatorNode
        • com.cafean.client.ui.navigator.NavigatorRootNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NavigatorRoot, java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, javax.swing.tree.MutableTreeNode, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode
    public class NavigatorRootNode
extends NavigatorNode
implements NavigatorRoot
    This node is the root of the navigator. This node never appears inside the navigator, but is always expanded. It contains the PluginNodes that display open plugins in the navigator.
